  "texts": [
    "In general, these variations likely reflect the different intended uses, regulatory environments, and community norms each service is designed to serve.",
    "It underscores the importance of understanding the specific content policies of each chatbot service to ensure compliance and responsible use.",
    "In the rest of this paper, we primarily focus on four key categories prohibited by all the LLM services.",
    "We use Illegal, Harmful, Priavcy and Adult to refer to the four categories for simplicity.Finding 1: There are four common prohibited scenarios restricted by all the mainstream LLM chatbot service providers: illegal usage against law, generation of harmful or abusive contents, violation of rights and privacy, and generation of adult contents.",
    "B. Jailbreak Effectiveness (RQ2)We delve deeper to evaluate the effectiveness of existing jailbreak prompts across different LLM chatbot services."
  ]
